{"id":17918,"date":"2022-12-31T04:17:55","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:17:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/lexus-es-300h-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-voi-moi-truong.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:17:55","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:17:55","slug":"lexus-es-300h-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-voi-moi-truong-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/lexus-es-300h-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-voi-moi-truong-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Lexus ES 300h \u2013 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<ul class=\"social_left\">\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"myvne_save_for_later\" data-token=\"19b6076c5eb37053b961aa4cf6af081b\" data-article-id=\"4534799\" title=\"L\u01b0u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft\">\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li_comment\"><span class=\"number_cmt txt_num_comment num_cmt_detail\" data-type=\"comment\" data-objecttype=\"7\" data-objectid=\"4534799\"><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span class=\"tip\">Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h1><span style=\"color:rgb(33,33,33);\">Lexus ES 300h \u2013 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/h1>\n<h2>Xe sang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 l\u1edbn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb g\u1eafn m\u00e1c t\u1ed1n x\u0103ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.  Lexus hybrid ra \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a l\u1ea1i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.<\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-130-mobile-6550-1668677402\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-130-8270-1668677402.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-130-mobile-6550-1668677402.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-130-mobile-6550-1668677402-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-130-mobile-6550-1668677402-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-130-mobile-6550-1668677402.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-142-mobile-5561-1668677402\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-142-8841-1668677402.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-142-mobile-5561-1668677402.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_528_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-142-mobile-5561-1668677402-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-142-mobile-5561-1668677402-600x406.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-142-mobile-5561-1668677402.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang b\u1eb1ng dung t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1.  Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb, v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n, xe sang ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 V6 ho\u1eb7c V8, dung t\u00edch xi-lanh ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb 3.0 tr\u1edf l\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.  Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n cung nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u00f3a th\u1ea1ch, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00ean th\u00ec c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe sang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cXu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 dung t\u00edch l\u1edbn \u0111ang tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh \u00f4t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i chia s\u1ebb.  \u201cGi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe sang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u, trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, xe sang gi\u1edd ph\u1ea3i xanh h\u01a1n, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u\u201d.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" title=\"1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443489_387_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg 1900w\"><\/p>\n<p>Lexus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00e3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng xe hybrid th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.  B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc RX SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2004, m\u00e0u xanh lam c\u1ee7a logo hybrid hi\u1ec7n bao tr\u00f9m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.  N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, xe hybrid chi\u1ebfm g\u1ea7n 35% t\u1ed5ng doanh s\u1ed1 Lexus to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 260.000 chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1n ra, t\u0103ng 10% so v\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020. <\/p>\n<p>M\u1eabu sedan h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 trung ES l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai m\u1eabu xe d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ea1t 189.000 chi\u1ebfc hybrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi RX.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-136-mobile-7873-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-136-4655-1668677402.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-136-mobile-7873-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443490_755_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-136-mobile-7873-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-136-mobile-7873-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-136-mobile-7873-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-115-mobile-7597-1668155573\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-115-3080-1668155573.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-115-mobile-7597-1668155573.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443490_492_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-115-mobile-7597-1668155573-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-115-mobile-7597-1668155573-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-115-mobile-7597-1668155573.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-127-mobile-2245-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-127-6138-1668677403.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-127-mobile-2245-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443490_935_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-127-mobile-2245-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-127-mobile-2245-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-127-mobile-2245-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u201cLexus hybrid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe sang, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 Trung \u0110\u00f4ng sinh s\u1ed1ng. RX hybrid d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean di chuy\u1ec3n, c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng doanh nh\u00e2n tr\u1ebb th\u00ec ES hybrid l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua\u201d, anh Minh Nguy\u1ec5n (35 tu\u1ed5i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i), c\u1ef1u du h\u1ecdc sinh M\u1ef9, hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 CEO m\u1ed9t startup c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, chia s\u1ebb.  \u201cKhi v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c, t\u00f4i ch\u1ecdn mua ES 300h v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u1edf M\u1ef9\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>\u1ede th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Lexus ES c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb d\u00f2ng LS nh\u01b0ng mang d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 thao h\u01a1n.  Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf L-Finesse mang t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ecdc, gi\u1ea3m l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u.  \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh con su\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nan h\u00ecnh v\u00e2y c\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Lexus th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" title=\"1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_948_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg 1900w\"><\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng Full LED v\u1edbi c\u00e1c micro LED, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh lu\u1ed3ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y ch\u00f3i m\u1eaft cho c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.  \u0110\u00e8n ch\u1ea1y ban ng\u00e0y h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef L \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng, \u200b\u200bt\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED v\u1edbi hoa v\u0103n 3D nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef L. <\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb h\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea5t th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua c\u1ed9t C k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ed1p l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb d\u00f2ng sportback, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb CEO tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00edch th\u00fa nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-137-mobile-2563-1668155574\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-137-4884-1668155574.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-137-mobile-2563-1668155574.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_118_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-137-mobile-2563-1668155574-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-137-mobile-2563-1668155574-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-137-mobile-2563-1668155574.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-134-jpg-mobile-6978-1668155574\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-134-JPG-2716-1668155574.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-134-jpg-mobile-6978-1668155574.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443491_952_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-134-jpg-mobile-6978-1668155574-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-134-jpg-mobile-6978-1668155574-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-134-jpg-mobile-6978-1668155574.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u1ede n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, ES 300h l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da b\u00e1n anilin cao c\u1ea5p.  B\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u1eeda v\u1edbi con ch\u00f3 g\u00f3c b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7.  Gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n 10 h\u01b0\u1edbng, \u0111\u1ec7m l\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9nh 4 h\u01b0\u1edbng, nh\u1edb 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u01b0\u1edfi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t.  H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n 8 \u0111\u1ed9, c\u00f3 r\u00e8m che ri\u00eang t\u01b0, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u1ee3t. <\/p>\n<p>V\u00f4 l\u0103ng 3 ch\u1ea5u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi, \u1ed1p g\u1ed7 Shimamoku cao c\u1ea5p, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c ph\u00edm ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, l\u1eaby chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean v\u00f4 l\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" title=\"1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_482_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg 1900w\"><\/p>\n<p>ES 300h t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 2,5 l\u00edt c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 176 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n 120 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c cho t\u1ed5ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 214 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 300 Nm.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng eCVT ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch theo d\u00f5i th\u00f3i quen ga v\u00e0 phanh tr\u00ean c\u00e1c cung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau. <\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i 3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0 Normal (b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng), Eco (Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m) v\u00e0 Sport (Th\u1ec3 thao), ES 300h c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n EV, k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t b\u1eb1ng tay th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t n\u00fat b\u1ea5m.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-100-jpg-mobile-9549-1668155574\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-100-JPG-3468-1668155574.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-100-jpg-mobile-9549-1668155574.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_453_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-100-jpg-mobile-9549-1668155574-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-100-jpg-mobile-9549-1668155574-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-100-jpg-mobile-9549-1668155574.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-69-jpg-mobile-5101-1668155574\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-69-JPG-7067-1668155574.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-69-jpg-mobile-5101-1668155574.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_572_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-69-jpg-mobile-5101-1668155574-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-69-jpg-mobile-5101-1668155574-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-69-jpg-mobile-5101-1668155574.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-56-jpg-mobile-6937-1668155574\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-56-JPG-8065-1668155574.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-56-jpg-mobile-6937-1668155574.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443492_774_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-56-jpg-mobile-6937-1668155574-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-56-jpg-mobile-6937-1668155574-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-56-jpg-mobile-6937-1668155574.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u201cT\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, trong khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh mild-hybrid h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c th\u00ec Lexus trang b\u1ecb c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh full-hybrid cho lo\u1ea1t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 xe Lexus hybrid c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, PGS.  TS \u0110\u00e0m Ho\u00e0ng Ph\u00fac, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng khoa K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u00f4 t\u00f4, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc B\u00e1ch khoa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho bi\u1ebft. <\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i linh ho\u1ea1t trong nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u kho\u1ea3ng 30-40% so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.  Xe ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00edt x\u0103ng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-73-jpg-mobile-1458-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-73-JPG-2805-1668677403.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-73-jpg-mobile-1458-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443493_996_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-73-jpg-mobile-1458-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-73-jpg-mobile-1458-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-73-jpg-mobile-1458-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-97-jpg-mobile-6133-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-97-JPG-3444-1668677403.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-97-jpg-mobile-6133-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443493_353_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-97-jpg-mobile-6133-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-97-jpg-mobile-6133-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-97-jpg-mobile-6133-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>V\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia cho r\u1eb1ng, khi \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u1eddi gian s\u1ea1c, h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng tr\u1ea1m s\u1ea1c\u2026 th\u00ec hybrid l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n sang \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cHybrid l\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 xe xanh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 xe xanh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0: mild-hybrid, hybrid v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c pin nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u\u201d, \u00f4ng chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-84-mobile-8844-1668155575\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-84-1978-1668155575.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-84-mobile-8844-1668155575.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443493_833_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-84-mobile-8844-1668155575-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-84-mobile-8844-1668155575-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-84-mobile-8844-1668155575.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-82-jpg-mobile-3710-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-82-JPG-8002-1668677403.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-82-jpg-mobile-3710-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443493_917_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-82-jpg-mobile-3710-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-82-jpg-mobile-3710-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-82-jpg-mobile-3710-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-80-jpg-mobile-8652-1668677403\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-80-JPG-4113-1668677403.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-80-jpg-mobile-8652-1668677403.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_971_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-80-jpg-mobile-8652-1668677403-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-80-jpg-mobile-8652-1668677403-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-80-jpg-mobile-8652-1668677403.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-92-jpg-mobile-5822-1668155575\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-92-JPG-4388-1668155575.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-92-jpg-mobile-5822-1668155575.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_273_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-92-jpg-mobile-5822-1668155575-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-92-jpg-mobile-5822-1668155575-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-92-jpg-mobile-5822-1668155575.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>So v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, Lexus ES hybrid n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p 4,6 l\u00edt\/100 km theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t.  Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng 10 l\/100 km.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cTi\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1ecf khi t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua ES 300h, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 hybrid cho c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t y\u00ean t\u0129nh b\u00ean trong cabin, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u201ct\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t\u201d v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u00e2m thanh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. \u1ed3n \u00e0o,\u201d Minh Nguyen n\u00f3i.  \u201cS\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong sang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0a Lexus v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.\u201d<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" title=\"1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_315_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg 1900w\"><\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng, ES 300h \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus trang b\u1ecb g\u00f3i Hybrid Acoustics s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00e1ch \u00e2m 3 l\u1edbp gi\u00fap h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh cho khoang h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch.  . <\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1ch \u00e2m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh l\u00e0 hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, khi v\u1ecb CEO tr\u1ebb h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y l\u00e1i xe gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-9-mobile-9235-1668705378\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-9-1176-1668705378.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-9-mobile-9235-1668705378.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443494_971_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-9-mobile-9235-1668705378-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-9-mobile-9235-1668705378-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-9-mobile-9235-1668705378.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-11-mobile-3599-1668705378\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-11-5273-1668705378.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-11-mobile-3599-1668705378.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443495_210_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-11-mobile-3599-1668705378-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-11-mobile-3599-1668705378-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-11-mobile-3599-1668705378.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh xa ph\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac, Minh Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng xanh, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i V\u01b0\u1eddn qu\u1ed1c gia Ba V\u00ec, c\u00e1ch H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kho\u1ea3ng 60 km.  Tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn xe ES 300h, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u01b0\u1eddn x\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3ng nguy\u00ean sinh, r\u1eebng th\u00f4ng, nh\u00e0 th\u1edd Ph\u00e1p c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh, \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian xanh t\u1ea1i resort 5 sao Melia Ba V\u00ec Mountain Retreat.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc ES 300h c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb CEO tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u1ed3n \u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u1ef1 t\u0129nh l\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-14-jpg-mobile-3750-1668155576\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-14-JPG-1920-1668155576.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-14-jpg-mobile-3750-1668155576.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443495_408_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-14-jpg-mobile-3750-1668155576-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-14-jpg-mobile-3750-1668155576-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-14-jpg-mobile-3750-1668155576.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-25-jpg-mobile-6974-1668155576\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-25-JPG-8470-1668155576.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-25-jpg-mobile-6974-1668155576.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443495_304_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-25-jpg-mobile-6974-1668155576-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-25-jpg-mobile-6974-1668155576-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-25-jpg-mobile-6974-1668155576.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-34-jpg-mobile-2204-1668155576\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-34-JPG-2616-1668155576.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-34-jpg-mobile-2204-1668155576.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_522_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-34-jpg-mobile-2204-1668155576-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-34-jpg-mobile-2204-1668155576-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-34-jpg-mobile-2204-1668155576.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-es300h-40-jpg-mobile-5053-1668155576\" alt=\"Lexus-ES300h-40-JPG-4133-1668155576.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-40-jpg-mobile-5053-1668155576.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_132_Lexus-ES-300h-\u2013-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-40-jpg-mobile-5053-1668155576-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-40-jpg-mobile-5053-1668155576-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-es300h-40-jpg-mobile-5053-1668155576.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 2021, doanh s\u1ed1 xe xanh c\u1ee7a Lexus \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 2 tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfc, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n t\u1ea1i 90 qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 v\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5.  T\u1eeb n\u0103m 2005 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, d\u00f2ng xe xanh Lexus \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m 19 tri\u1ec7u t\u1ea5n CO2, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a 300.000 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u01a1 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng trong 15 n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a xe hybrid Lexus khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n v\u00ec quy m\u00f4 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Lexus trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe hybrid h\u1ea1ng sang kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 hay c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7.  \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00ed h\u1eadu \u2013 v\u1ed1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb th\u00f3i quen h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y: di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_72_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg\" alt=\"Lexus Es 300 - \u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" title=\"1672443496_72_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_72_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_72_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672443496_72_lexus-es-300h-e28093-dinh-nghia-xe-sang-than-thien.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Lexus Es 300 \u2013 \u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Quang Anh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">\u1ea2nh v\u00e0 video: TMV<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">Lexus Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch gia h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh m\u1edbi cho phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ES m\u1edbi, \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 15\/11\/2022. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh cho xe t\u0103ng t\u1eeb 3 n\u0103m (kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n km) l\u00ean 5 n\u0103m (kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n km) cho xe v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 t\u00f9ng, t\u1eeb 5 n\u0103m (kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n km) \u0111\u1ebfn 7 n\u0103m (kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n km).  km) cho pin hybrid. <\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i Lexus ES 300h \u2013 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe sang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Xe sang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 l\u1edbn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb g\u1eafn m\u00e1c t\u1ed1n x\u0103ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Lexus hybrid ra \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a l\u1ea1i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a xe [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16018,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17918"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17918"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17918\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16018"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17918"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17918"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17918"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}